---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Snake Minimalist Game"
  description="Privacy policy for Snake Minimalist Game, detailing data handling practices for the Google Play Store release."
  showCanvas={false}
>
  <div class="inner-page">

    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="bc-link">andreschipol.com</a>
      <span class="bc-sep">/</span>
      <a href="/sideprojects" class="bc-link">Side Projects</a>
      <span class="bc-sep">/</span>
      <a href="/sideprojects/snake-minimalist-game/" class="bc-link">Snake Minimalist Game</a>
      <span class="bc-sep">/</span>
      <span class="bc-current">Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="inner-header">
      <p class="inner-eyebrow">Legal · Snake Minimalist Game</p>
      <h1 class="inner-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="inner-meta">Last updated: 22 October 2025</p>
      <p class="inner-sub">
        Snake Minimalist Game respects your privacy and is committed to protecting any
        information that may be collected while using the app.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="doc-body">

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">01</span> Information we collect</h2>
        <p>
          Snake Minimalist Game does not collect, store, or share personal information from users.
          The game does not request registration, name, email, or any other identifiable data.
        </p>
        <p>
          If third-party services are used (such as Google Play Games, AdMob, or others), those
          services may collect data according to their own privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">02</span> Use of information</h2>
        <p>If non-personal information is collected (e.g. anonymous statistics or performance data), it will only be used to:</p>
        <ul class="doc-list">
          <li>Improve the gameplay experience.</li>
          <li>Analyze bugs or technical issues.</li>
          <li>Optimize the overall performance of the app.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">03</span> Cookies and similar technologies</h2>
        <p>
          Snake Minimalist Game does not use cookies directly. However, external services (such as
          analytics or advertising providers) may use cookies or anonymous identifiers in line with
          their own policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">04</span> Third-party links</h2>
        <p>
          The app may include links or integrations with external services. Once you access those
          links, Snake Minimalist Game has no control over their content or policies — please review
          their respective privacy statements.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">05</span> Security</h2>
        <p>
          We are committed to keeping the app as secure as possible. Even though personal information
          is not handled, we apply good security practices to prevent unauthorized access or issues
          that may affect the user experience.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">06</span> Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy may be updated at any time. Please review it periodically. Any
          modifications will be published on this page or within the app.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="doc-section">
        <h2 class="doc-heading"><span class="doc-num">07</span> Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at
          <a class="doc-mailto" href="mailto:andy.c.chipol@gmail.com">andy.c.chipol@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <footer class="doc-footer">
      <p>Thank you for playing Snake Minimalist Game.</p>
      <a href="/sideprojects/snake-minimalist-game/" class="doc-back">← Back to project</a>
    </footer>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .inner-page {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
    font-size: .72rem;
    color: var(--dust);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .bc-link { color: var(--sage); text-decoration: none; transition: opacity .2s; }
  .bc-link:hover { opacity: .7; }
  .bc-sep { color: var(--rule); }
  .bc-current { color: var(--dust); }

  .inner-header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .inner-eyebrow {
    font-size: .62rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dust);
    margin-bottom: .75rem;
  }

  .inner-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }

  .inner-meta {
    font-size: .75rem;
    color: var(--dust);
    margin-bottom: .75rem;
  }

  .inner-sub {
    font-size: .95rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .doc-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .doc-section {
    padding: 1.75rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: .92rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.8;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .75rem;
  }

  .doc-section:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }

  .doc-heading {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .65rem;
  }

  .doc-num {
    font-size: .6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    background: var(--cream-2);
    color: var(--dust);
    padding: .2rem .45rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .doc-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .45rem;
  }

  .doc-list li {
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .doc-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--sage);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .doc-mailto {
    color: var(--sage);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sage-lt);
    transition: opacity .2s;
  }
  .doc-mailto:hover { opacity: .7; }

  .doc-footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-size: .82rem;
    color: var(--dust);
  }

  .doc-back {
    color: var(--sage);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: .8rem;
    transition: opacity .2s;
  }
  .doc-back:hover { opacity: .7; }
</style>
